        - how many repeats to schedule
        - will the amount vary? is there a range it should fall in?
          - that lends to an upper and lower amount due so like if its my internet its fixed but electric might be lower=80 upper=160 actual=143 or something
        - normal fields and stuff like name/due date/etc
          - repeat schedule
        ======= indev
        * so we start with an "expenses" table 
          - add to it
          - edit things
          - view the compiled projections
      </pre>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
